%5CnSo%2C%20what%20is%20a%20data%20product%3F%20%5Cn%5Cn!%5BData%20Products%20and%20their%20Analytical%20Capabilities%5D(https%3A%2F%2Fdev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fuploads%2Farticles%2Fh5y2584oxjpc2sp1qfuc.jpeg)%5CnData%20Products%20and%20their%20Analytical%20Capabilities%20%5BSource%5D(https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lionbase.nyc%2Fwhats-a-data-product-cd33f4a89946)%5Cn%5CnA%20data%20product%20is%20an%20application%20or%20tool%20that%20leverages%20data%20and%20statistical%20algorithms%20to%20improve%20decision%20making%20processes%20and%20aid%20people%20making%20business%20decisions.%5Cn%5CnData%20products%20help%20businesses%20make%20informed%20decisions%20by%20providing%20them%20with%20the%20necessary%20information%20and%20insight%20from%20data.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20gives%20them%20competitive%20advantages%20in%20serving%20and%20providing%20for%20the%20needs%20of%20their%20customers.%20Examples%20of%20data%20products%20are%20Salesforce%E2%80%99s%20Einstein%20AI%2C%20Google%20Analytics%2C%20Tableau%20Prep%2C%20and%20several%20others.%20All%20of%20these%20tools%20make%20their%20users%20more%20productive.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Improving%20Productivity%20Using%20Data%20Products%5Cn%5CnIt%20is%20interesting%20that%20data%20products%20make%20people%20and%20organizations%20more%20productive%20in%20their%20day%20to%20day%20activities.%20The%20secret%20behind%20these%20products%20revolves%20around%20how%20data%20products%20arrange%2C%20organize%2C%20and%20present%20data%20to%20give%20insight%20that%20helps%20in%20making%20decisions.%20Improving%20productivity%20revolves%20around%20sorting%2C%20estimation%2C%20prediction%2C%20recommendation%2C%20automation%2C%20and%20many%20other%20abilities%20of%20data%20products%2C%20which%20are%20explained%20below.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%23%20Sorting%20Items%20and%20Users%5Cn%5CnData%20products%20ensure%20productivity%20by%20sorting%20information%20provided%20to%20users.%20That%20means%2C%20they%20group%20items%20or%20people%20based%20on%20their%20common%20feature(s).%20This%20arrangement%20ensures%20productivity%20by%20making%20dealing%20with%20such%20information%20easy%20for%20users.%20For%20example%2C%20reviews%20for%20a%20product%20may%20be%20grouped%20into%20%E2%80%9Cexcellent%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfair%E2%80%9D%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20reviews%20from%20the%20users.%20Sorting%20the%20reviews%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20discover%20excellent%2C%20fair%2C%20and%20poor%20reviews%20from%20users%20without%20wasting%20time.%20%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%23%20Racking%20Items%20and%20Activities%5CnRacking%20items%20and%20user%20activities%20is%20another%20secret%20to%20improving%20productivity%20using%20data%20products%20because%20it%20gives%20insight%20that%20helps%20individuals%20and%20organizations%20make%20quick%20and%20informed%20decisions.%20%5Cn%5CnFor%20example%2C%20different%20products%20from%20a%20company%20may%20be%20ranked%20according%20to%20their%20likelihood%20of%20contributing%20to%20sales%20or%20the%20number%20of%20the%20pieces%20sold%20within%20a%20given%20time.%20Thereafter%2C%20decision%20makers%20can%20decide%20on%20which%20product%20to%20focus%20on%20or%20kill%20to%20satisfy%20the%20interests%20of%20their%20customers%20and%20maximize%20profits.%20Ranking%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20ensures%20productivity%20by%20reducing%20the%20effort%20and%20time%20spent%20in%20making%20decisions.%20The%20necessary%20insight%20is%20already%20provided%20by%20data%20products.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%23%20Suggesting%2FRecommending%20Items%20or%20Actions%5Cn%5CnData%20products%20can%20identify%20opportunities%20based%20on%20data%20and%20statistical%20decision%20making%20algorithms%20to%20make%20suggestions%20for%20the%20end%20users.%20Such%20suggestions%20are%20backed%20by%20data%20and%20can%20enable%20product%20managers%2C%20user%20researchers%2C%20and%20business%20leaders%20to%20identify%20the%20wants%20and%20needs%20of%20their%20users%20or%20the%20challenges%20of%20the%20organizations.%20They%20will%20be%20more%20equipped%20with%20insight%20backed%20by%20data%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions.%20%5Cn%5CnFor%20instance%2C%20a%20data%20product%20may%20recommend%20categories%20of%20customers%20that%20the%20company%20needs%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20based%20on%20purchases%20on%20their%20platforms.%20This%20suggesting%20is%20another%20key%20way%20to%20improve%20productivity%20because%20it%20makes%20it%20easy%20for%20decision%20makers%20to%20decide%20what%20actions%20they%20can%20take%20to%20improve%20their%20business.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%23%20Estimating%20Values%5Cn%5CnEstimating%20values%20of%20activities%20on%20a%20platform%20provide%20useful%20information%20for%20the%20decision%20making%20process.%20A%20data%20product%20can%20estimate%20several%20factors%20such%20as%20demography%2C%20location%2C%20language%2C%20interests%2C%20interactions%2C%20engagement%20and%20much%20more%20to%20provide%20in-depth%20details%20and%20valuable%20insight%20to%20support%20the%20decision%20making%20process%20of%20an%20individual%20or%20organization.%20Providing%20a%20detailed%20estimate%20supports%20decision%20makers%20to%20be%20more%20productive%20in%20process%20and%20outcome.%20Data%20products%20such%20as%20Google%20Analytics%20provide%20estimates%20on%20the%20traffic%20of%20websites.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%23%20Predicting%20Possibilities%5Cn%5CnA%20data%20product%20can%20make%20predictions%20backed%20by%20data%20to%20inform%20product%20managers%2C%20user%20researchers%2C%20and%20business%20leaders%20about%20possibilities%20they%20might%20not%20be%20aware%20of.%20Such%20information%20will%20help%20them%20make%20informed%20decisions%20to%20achieve%20productive%20processes%20and%20outcomes.%20It%20could%20predict%20actions%20and%20reactions%E2%80%94churning%2C%20fraud%2C%20buying%2C%20selling%E2%80%94of%20certain%20groups%20of%20users%20based%20on%20their%20characteristics%2C%20interactions%2C%20age%2C%20location%2C%20unusual%20activities%2C%20and%20other%20factors.%20Such%20predictions%20could%20help%20decision%20makers%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%20against%20possible%20occurrences.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%23%20Automating%20Decisions%5Cn%5CnThe%20abilities%20of%20data%20products%20to%20sort%2C%20estimate%2C%20recommend%2C%20and%20predict%20possibilities%20necessitate%20decision%20automation.%20Some%20decision%20making%20processes%20could%20be%20automated%20to%20free%20up%20human%20intervention.%20These%20decisions%20could%20be%20to%20logout%20users%20that%20are%20suspected%20of%20performing%20unwanted%20activities%20such%20as%20spam%20and%20fraud.%20Facebook%20uses%20such%20automation%20to%20lock%20out%20suspected%20accounts.%20%5Cn%5CnEffective%20decision%20making%20automation%20helps%20decision%20makers%20get%20more%20time%20to%20deal%20with%20more%20important%20decisions%20that%20require%20human%20intervention%2C%20leading%20to%20an%20improvement%20in%20output.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Conclusion%5Cn%5CnAs%20the%20business%20terrain%20is%20getting%20more%20competitive%20and%20business%20activities%20becoming%20more%20complex%20as%20a%20result%20of%20growth%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20have%20access%20to%20data%20and%20statistical%20insights%20to%20make%20informed%20decisions.%20%5Cn%5CnSorting%2C%20estimation%2C%20recommendation%2C%20and%20the%20other%20methods%20mentioned%20above%20are%20the%20secret%20to%20improving%20productivity%20using%20data%20products%20because%20they%20provide%20us%20with%20the%20necessary%20insights%20that%20enable%20product%20managers%2C%20user%20researchers%2C%20and%20business%20leaders%20to%20be%20more%20productive%20in%20decision%20making%20processes%20and%20final%20decisions.%22%2C%22id%22%3A3%2C%22deleted%22%3Afalse%2C%22restoredAt%22%3A%222023-01-07T15%3A06%3A13.293Z%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20make%20%242000%20write%20technical%20articles%22%2C%22slug%22%3A%22how-to-make-2000-write-technical-articles%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tags%22%3A%22%22%2C%2