5Cn%5CnBut%20wait%20a%20minute%2C%20I%20still%20want%20to%20appreciate%20those%20first%20articles%20I%20found%20%E2%80%93%20it%20took%20their%20authors%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20and%20effort%20to%20put%20them%20together.%20And%20as%20a%20writer%2C%20I%20appreciated%20the%20information%20they%20shared%20because%20they%20provided%20a%20list%20of%20companies%20I%20could%20write%20for.%5Cn%5CnJust%20like%20them%2C%20to%20help%20you%20avoid%20stress%20and%20stop%20wasting%20time%2C%20I%20have%20compiled%20a%20list%20of%20companies%20you%20can%20write%20for.%20After%20the%20list%2C%20we'll%20dive%20into%20how%20you%20can%20make%20the%20most%20of%20writing%20technical%20articles%20for%20money.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%20Publications%20that%20Pay%20You%20For%20Technical%20Articles%5Cn%5CnBefore%20I%20show%20you%20how%20to%20get%20yourself%20into%20the%20game%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20you%20know%20the%20platforms%20you%20can%20write%20for.%20So%20I%20have%20curated%20some%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20platforms%20that%20will%20pay%20you%20money%20to%20write%20technical%20articles%20for%20them.%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Twilio%20(up%20to%20%24500)%5Cn%5CnTwilio%20pays%20up%20to%20%24500%20per%20article%20and%20you're%20not%20required%20to%20use%20any%20of%20Twilio's%20packages.%20They%20take%20articles%20about%20general%20development.%20%5BApply%20here%5D(https%3A%2F%2Fgo.twilio.com%2Ftwilio-voices%2F).%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Clubhouse.io%20(%24350-%24600)%5Cn%5CnClubhouse.io%20pays%20%24350-%24600%20per%20article.%20They%20take%20articles%20about%20team%20collaboration%2C%20software%20development%2C%20and%20general%20how-tos.%20%5BApply%20here%5D(https%3A%2F%2Fclubhouse.io%2Fclubhouse-write-earn-give-program%2F).%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20TestDriven.io%20(up%20to%20%24500)%5Cn%5CnTestDriven.io%20pays%20up%20to%20%24500%20per%20article.%20They%20publish%20articles%20that%20teach%20testing%2C%20scaling%2C%20and%20application%20optimization%20with%20web%20technologies.%20%5Cn%5Cn%23%23%23%20Honey%20B